◇ Traveling too far into the forest in [[Level 300]] will bring wanderers to Orange Offices.<br>
◇ After spending 2 hours in [[Level 17]] or getting scurvy while in the level will cause the next door they enter to be directly linked to Level 208.<br>
◇ Orange lights in [[Level 161]], if looked at for too long, will send wanderers to Level 208.




