◇ A dark red door leads to [[Level 959|somewhere you don't want to know]].<br>
◇ Small chunks of sandstone will send one to [[Level 209]], however these chunks are somewhat rare.<br>
◇ Attempting to noclip through the walls will often lead one here to [[Level 960]].<br>



